6220/extras/d960afd31400ed2fb33418be88b6f2cc.poster.avif?t=1589862505\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/d960afd31400ed2fb33418be88b6f2cc.webm?t=1589862505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/d960afd31400ed2fb33418be88b6f2cc.mp4?t=1589862505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Flexible movement and invincible jumping can effectively avoid the attack of enemies and organs</strong><br><br>Break the supply box to get all kinds of props, shields and bullets. Continuous jumping can help you defeat enemies and save the earth<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/4f3274ddcd07d5dfc565a3ba00bbd3e3.poster.avif?t=1589862505\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/4f3274ddcd07d5dfc565a3ba00bbd3e3.webm?t=1589862505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/4f3274ddcd07d5dfc565a3ba00bbd3e3.mp4?t=1589862505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Seize the opportunity to break the fort is the key to customs clearance, and at the same time, continuously defeat the enemy can increase the score<br><br>Challenge the more crazy enemies, full of bullets and traps on the screen, and gain infinite sense of achievement<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/c7ddb3eb9f982426bec859a8d705bd85.poster.avif?t=1589862505\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256220/extras/c7ddb3eb9f982426bec859a8d7